INSERT INTO `gtek_posts` VALUES (23, 1, '2015-11-18 19:46:39', '2015-11-18 19:46:39', 'When Scraptastic Club engaged us in 2015, they had an existing site that had only recently been completed. The issue was that the quality of the design was low and the site was riddled with bugs. GloboTek was tasked with redesigning very aspect of the brand and developing a new, easy to manage site that was quick and reliable.\r\n\r\nScraptastic Club had a few very interesting features requests such as loyalty reward points and a monthly subscription box. Each month, users were required to pick which product they would like to receive from a curated selection of 3 boxes. Purchases accrued points which would translate into cash discounts on future purchases.\r\n\r\nWe worked closely with the business owner to understand the target market and develop a design that was appealing to them. Scraptastic Club had good brand awareness in the USA and a strong following so it was important. As such, getting the message right was essential to attract new customers from competitors. Furthermore, the site needed to make the process of managing orders and dispatching subscriber boxes simpler and quicker. All of these was achieved and led to higher conversion rates.', 'Scraptastic Club', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur et vestibulum arcu. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'scraptastic-club', '', '', '2019-05-03 12:49:01', '2019-05-03 11:49:01', '', 0, 'http://globotek.local/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=23', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `gtek_posts` VALUES (24, 1, '2019-02-18 19:46:38', '2019-02-18 19:46:38', 'We were approached by Bosio Inc through the Codeable platform in the Autumn of 2015. GloboTek was asked to assist with the development work to rebuild the <a href=\"https://poweryoga.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Power Yoga</a> website. Power Yoga produces video Yoga classes, hosted on their site. Previously, multiple platforms had been used to do this, such as Hubspot for user subscriptions.  As a result, the new site’s objective was a simple one; to unify and simplify the management of the products under one website.  GloboTek was provided with a design and engaged to build a bespoke WordPress theme. As the visual aspect of the site was developed, the data structure was mapped out and the necessary plugins identified to provide the required functionality\r\n\r\nPrimary objectives of the build revolved around making the site simple to manage and create a reliable, fast, future proof website! Ajax search has been heavily utilised to provides a smooth user experience when browsing the library and Ajax loaded paginated pages offer greater benefit for Search Engine Ranking.\r\n\r\nAs part of the ongoing growth strategy, GloboTek partnered with Power Yoga in 2018 to implement a raft of new features. Social networking and a redesigned and restructured video library formed the core of the upgrade. New, powerful features have been incorporated into the library that allow the site owner’s to create curated series of videos for users to follow via Chumly’s eLearning extension. Chumly’s activity feed and posting capabilities, a truly unique commenting system has been implemented. This system encourages discussion and community on the site.', 'Power Yoga', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'power-yoga', '', '', '2019-05-01 11:46:54', '2019-05-01 10:46:54', '', 0, 'http://globotek.local/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=24', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `gtek_posts` VALUES (25, 1, '2015-02-18 19:46:26', '2015-02-18 19:46:26', 'GloboTek\'s task was extensive with the RoomieMatch Us build. The brief called for us to handle every aspect of design and development to launch the company. We had to perform large amounts of research to establish how we would build the required functionality and where we would get the property listings from. As a result, the decision was made to use BuddyPress for the networking side of things and bespoke tools for the property listing side of things.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'RoomieMatch Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'roomiematch', '', '', '2019-05-01 11:34:28', '2019-05-01 10:34:28', '', 0, 'http://globotek.local/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=25', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0);
