look for when hiring or explain the difficulties that face someone hiring an individual or company. Those issue will be discussed in detail in future&nbsp;articles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>If you would like to arrange a consultation or have any questions that you feel we may be able to help answer, then please do not hesitate to <a href=\"https://globotek.net/contact-us\">get in touch</a>. We\'re here to help!</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Who to hire - a freelancer, an agency or an employee?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '63-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-03 15:10:15', '2019-04-03 14:10:15', '', 63, 'http://globotek.local/63-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
