INSERT INTO `gtek_posts` VALUES (364, 1, '2019-04-30 22:13:49', '2019-04-30 21:13:49', 'We were approached by Bosio Inc through the Codeable platform in the Autumn of 2015. GloboTek was asked to assist with the development work to rebuild the <a href=\"https://poweryoga.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Power Yoga</a> website. Power Yoga produces video Yoga classes, hosted on their site. Previously, multiple platforms had been used to do this, such as Hubspot for user subscriptions.  As a result, the new site’s objective was a simple one; to unify and simplify the management of the products under one website.  GloboTek was provided with a design &amp; engaged to build a bespoke WordPress theme. As the visual aspect of the site was developed, the data structure was mapped out &amp; the necessary plugins identified to provide the required functionality\n\nPrimary objectives of the build revolved around making the site simple to manage &amp; create a reliable, fast, future proof website! Ajax search has been heavily utilised to provides a smooth user experience when browsing the library &amp; Ajax loaded paginated pages offer greater benefit for Search Engine Ranking.\n\nAs part of the ongoing growth strategy, GloboTek partnered with Power Yoga in 2018 to implement a raft of new features. Social networking and a redesigned and restructured video library formed the core of the upgrade. New, powerful features have been incorporated into the library that allow the site owner’s to create curated series of videos for users to follow via Chumly’s eLearning extension. Chumly’s activity feed &amp; posting capabilities, a truly unique commenting system has been implemented. This system encourages discussion &amp; community on the site.', 'Power Yoga', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '24-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-04-30 22:13:49', '2019-04-30 21:13:49', '', 24, 'http://globotek.local/24-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
